tion or drizzled with syrup or honey for a sweet option.","<strong>Gluten free pumpkin fritters<\/strong>: replace the plain flour and baking powder with gluten free plain flour and gluten free baking powder. Proceed as per recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","35m","18 portions"]}